" Pentadactyl rc 
" ---
" Works in Firefox only.
"=====

" macro to set zoom on page load
" au PageLoadPre http|https zoom 120

" Command mode map
map <C-f> <right>
map <C-b> <left>

" FollowHints -- default is 0
"   1 -- prevents links from being followed without confirmation from
"        carriage return.
set fh=1
